verbose_text: In this paper, we evaluated the effects of probiotic preparation Bifid Triple Viable (Shanghai Xinyi pharmacy Inc., China) on immune function through measuring the expression of peripheral blood immunoglobulins, complements, and T cell subgroups, and colon mucosa IL-1beta, IL-10 and IgA protein expressions in patients with UC.
evidence: IL-1beta, IL-10 and IgA protein expressions
